<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<head>
<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
<title>持卡人回访</title>
<style type="text/css">
body{
	background:#f5f5f5;
	font: 14px "Arial",sans-serif;
}
#main{
	width:90%;
	margin:60px auto;
	padding:20px;
	border:1px solid #f2f1f1;
	border-radius: 5px;
	background:#fff;
	}
#transactions{
	font: 14px "Arial",sans-serif;
	line-height:25px;
    margin: 20px 10px 10px 0;  
}
table #transactions {
    clear: both;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    text-align: left;
}
table {
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    border: 1px solid #DDD;
	width: 95%;
	border-collapse: collapse;
    border-spacing: 0;
}
td{
	border: 1px solid #ddd;
	padding:10px;
	}

</style>
</head>

<body>
   <div id="main">
    <h2>Dear Customer,</h2>
    <p id="transactions">
    	We are a payment platform company. <br/>
    	Please check the following information of the order from our seller's website deals3c.com<br/>
	Deals3c is a mobile phone accessories mall, providing mobile phone-related gadgets and ancillary supplies.<br>
	We checked that you have placed the order from this website and needed to confirm you have bought correspondent product 
and the merchandise you received is described as the website.<br>
    </p><br/>
    <p id="transactions">
	Therefore, please answer:
    </p>
    <p id="transactions">
    	1. Have you visited our seller's websitec deals3c.com ?<br/>
    	A. Yes&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;B. No &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; C. If not, please tell us the original website you visited<br/>
    </p><br/>
    <p id="transactions">
    	2. The merchandise that you received was the same as the website described?<br/>
    	A. Yes&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;B.No&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;C.Not quite the same.<br/>
    </p><br/>
    <p id="transactions">
    	3.  What products you have received? Are you satisfied with the products you bought?<br/>
    	A. Phone-related accessories&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;B.Clothes&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; C. Others( Please tell us what product you have received)<br/>
    </p><br/>
    
    <table id="dataTable1" >
		<tbody>
		<tr>
		    <td width="20%">Name:</td>
		    <td>${name}</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
	    	<td>Order No.:</td>
	    	<td>${orderNo}</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
		    <td>Payment No:</td>
		    <td>${tradeNo}</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
	    	<td>Transaction Time：</td>
		    <td>${transDate}</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
		    <td>Amount:</td>
		    <td>${currency} ${amount}</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
	    	<td>Website：</td>
		    <td>${website}</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
	    	<td>Merchandise：</td>
		    <td>${merchandise}</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td>Forwarder agency:</td>
			<td>${agency}</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td>Tracking NO:</td>
			<td>${trackingNo}</td>
		</tr>
		
		</tbody>
        </table>
        
      <p>Thank you for your attention and wish you have a good day. </p>
      <h4>Customer Service Team</h4> 
      
    </div>
    
</body>
</html>
